(1992) and his Chapter 2 of <i>Magnetic Recording: the First
100 Years,</i> edited by Daniel et. al. (1999). </span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.0983333in; margin-bottom: 0.0625in"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt">2. On Poulsen see Begun's Chapter 1 (1949), and Mark
Clark "The Magnetic Recording Industry" (1992) and his
