(1999). </span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.0983333in; margin-bottom: 0.0625in"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt">3. On Sayville and the Navy, see Morton (1995) pp. 89-90. </span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.0983333in; margin-bottom: 0.0625in"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif"><span style="font-size: 10pt">4. On Stille and Begun see Begun's Chapter 1 (1949) and
Mark Clark's Chapter 4 of <i>Magnetic Recording: the First
